data.description: Welcome to one of the sweetest homes on the block.  This home is fenced in with a privacy fence and is situated on a large lot.  The back yard is very spacious and ideal for entertaining.  There is a one car garage and parking for additional vehicles.  The living room is nestled with a fireplace and have vaulted ceilings.  The carpet is less than three years old and is throughout the home.  You will find a family room that has plenty of cabinet space and perfect for entertaining that leads to the back patio.  Schedule an appointment to view this gem.  The refrigerator does not convey with the property.
